    "key": "533692d499c255ea648e6427334318eb5886746f12fa9a29e7fcc941db86f9b3",
    "original": " no longer has ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" no longer has \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "a0a4d5a0a49ec1f86c5178602a8c9170b39450f5963c5deb7da8a5d049c83ed6",
    "original": " now has ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" now has \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "ee2b0e3fedccfb27f1314f7ad644945caf5144b5678471689eefd7fb1075bc8e",
    "original": "I tell you, a wonderous lush oasis, golden roofs flimmering in the distance, rainbow colored birds ahead! Where I saw that? Well, it was on the road to %settlement%. I swear!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "76ff32f3d180495838e7c4c573552575d753fcf00c93a446e3b90d4b1c681a16",
    "original": "Mirage Sightings",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Name = \"Mirage Sightings\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3dd4372ace9bdd355c3c6ebd3ca939369e30878dbe20d8119d469a57e879ee31",
    "original": "Mirages can be seen occasionally in the deserts, and following them can lead to a fate way worse than getting lost in the desert.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "799f3ed6cf1a3b9f07f81a5de02ac61a4ea1e85378d3f697ee64b4d73a331d77",
    "original": "Some evils do not come in the dark of the night or hide in the shadows. They come out in the scorching sun, during the mid of day. Head on to %settlement% if you want to find out what I am talking about.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "1fd97c2ba2fca0d4b454e5816b481a3ec378082eb28a6fd54692280019c46061",
    "original": "The cracking heat and flickering air have caused a lot of mirage sightings with reportedly strange figures shuffling within them. ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"The cracking heat and flickering air have caused a lot of mirage sightings with reportedly strange figures shuffling within them. \""
  }
]